^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|This hand is very makable. You only have at most a diamond loser. As long as you manage your entries correctly  you have to set up spades, and make sure you don't lose control prematurely. Your best line is to duck a diamond at trick two. Then you can draw trumps, play the KQ of spades, ruff to get back to your hand, play the Ace of spades. |
