NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|If the Jack does not drop, you ruff a spade, and still have a trump to get back to your hand to cash your last spade. The trick is to not use up the trump in your hand too early, as those are your entries. Nevertheless, that was a  hard hand to play. Many people would have gone down. I am just pointing out how it could be made to educate everyone on expert technique. |
